{
  "stem": "22910.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were given bunk beds, where each person slept separately with straw for a mattress, which was heaven, and a-- and a blanket, and a straw pillow, so which was really heaven.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then towards the winter, they brought us coats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The coats that were taken from prisoners-- you know, our own coats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, there was one young woman who found her coat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And since it was such a beautiful one, they didn't want to believe her that was hers, because it's one way of getting a beautiful coat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I happen to know her from home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told them it was her coat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember when she had it made-- a beautiful coat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she did get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just hand out this, this, this, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But she did her coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And here again things didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was too long, shortened it, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the factory, there were some Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one Polish girl-- by the way, I really had a lot of luck-- one Polish girl decided I was her sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said she never had a sister and I'm her sister, which meant that she gave me a needle, thread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever I asked her for, she gave me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She give me a toothbrush and-- and toothpaste.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever I asked her, she said if I can it bring it, I'll-- I'll do so, which was illegal, again illegal, everything illegal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, so we were there, working like this, August, September, October, November, December, about five months, five and a half months.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the 1st of January, when it was so cold, it was terrible cold, we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard-- and this-- this is something really quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
